            <code class="function">in int gl_PatchVerticesIn;</code>
        </p></div><div class="refsect1"><a id="description"></a><h2>Description</h2><p>
            Available only in the tessellation control and evaluation languages, <code class="function">gl_PatchVerticesIn</code>
            contains the number of vertices in the input being processed by the shader. A single tessellation control or
            evaluation shader can read patches of differing sizes, and so th value of <code class="function">gl_PatchVertexIn</code>
            may differ between patches.
